      • showAuction

        @GetMapping(value="/auction")
public java.lang.String showAuction(@RequestParam
                                                                  java.lang.String id,
                                                                  @RequestParam(required=false)
                                                                  java.lang.String manuallyDo,

                                                                  java.lang.String bidAmount,
                                                                  org.springframework.ui.Model model)
        Endpoint used to render the auction's page.
        Parameters:
        manuallyDo - if present, this means to manually complete an ended auction
        bidAmount - if present, this means that the user requested to bid for the current auction
        id - the auction id from auction_info table

      • showAuctions

        @GetMapping(value="/auctions")
public java.lang.String showAuctions(org.springframework.ui.Model model)
        Endpoint used for retrieving the auction's of the website. If the user is an admin, it shows all the auctions (active, ended and not-validate ones), else it shows only the active ones.

      • showMyAuctions

        @GetMapping(value="/my-auctions")
public java.lang.String showMyAuctions(org.springframework.ui.Model model)
        Endpoint used to show the current user's auctions (active, ended and not-validated ones). If an admin accesses this, it will redirect to "/error".

      • showMyBids

        @GetMapping(value="/my-bids")
public java.lang.String showMyBids(org.springframework.ui.Model model)
        Endpoint used to retrieve the current logged in user bids. If the user is an admin, it redirects to "/error".
